To-Do List GUI Application - Python Tkinter

 Project Overview
This is a Graphical User Interface (GUI) To-Do List application developed using Python Tkinter. It allows users to:
- Add tasks
- Mark tasks as completed
- Delete tasks
- Persist tasks to a JSON file (`tasks.json`) for data storage between sessions

 Features
- GUI Interface: User-friendly and easy to navigate
-Task Completion: Mark tasks as done with a checkbox
-Task Deletion: Remove tasks from the list
- Persistent Storage: All tasks are saved in `tasks.json`
- Minimal & Clean Design

Tech Stack
- Python 3
- Tkinter for GUI
- JSON Module for storing tasks
